ABOUT pkgutils


  This directory contains pkgutils, a set of utilities (pkgadd, pkgrm,
  pkginfo), which are used for managing software packages.

  This is a fork of CRUX' pkgutils.

  The original sources can be downloaded from:

    1. https://crux.nu/gitweb/?p=tools/pkgutils.git;a=summary
    2. git://crux.nu/tools/pkgutils.git


  DEPENDENCIES

  All the following dependencies are required at build time:

    * g++
    * make(1p)
    * pod2man(1pm)
    * libarchive(3)


